#

Black Bean and Sweet Potato Bowl

40 min
$10
450 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 2

Dietary Tags:

VeganGluten-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main Dish

Tags:

HealthyEasyQuick

Description

A vibrant and nutritious bowl featuring hearty black beans and roasted sweet potatoes, topped with a zesty lime dressing.

Ingredients

  • sweet potatoes: 2 medium
  • black beans: 1 can (15 oz), drained and rinsed
  • corn: 1 cup, frozen or canned
  • red bell pepper: 1, diced
  • avocado: 1, diced
  • lime: 1, juiced
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • fresh cilantro: 1/4 cup, chopped
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
